    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "劇団★見、初公演演目会議～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Troupe★Hoshimi‚ first performance program meeting~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.2267120360999995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.4000451724
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "どんどんぱふぱふ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bom Bom Honk Honk~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4000451724,
      "endTime": 7.4371879736999995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.6438546498
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、私達がやる舞台の内容を\n話し合って決めるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So then‚ let’s discuss and decide\nwhat kind of stage we’re going to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.6438546498,
      "endTime": 12.8870747883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.0737414836
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "どんな舞台をやりたいか、座長の雫ちゃんの意見を\n聞かせて下さい。それを元に、うちが脚本に仕上げます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan‚ as the troupe leader‚ please tell us\nwhat kind of play you want. I’ll turn that into the script.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.0737414836,
      "endTime": 22.069841718699998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.2831747849
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "初めての舞台だから、シンプルに……脚本は、みんなが\n知ってる話をアレンジするくらいがいいと思う……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since it’s our first stage‚ something simple…\nI think adapting a story everyone knows would be good…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.2831747849,
      "endTime": 30.9831744035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.1965074698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "完全オリジナルより二次創作の方が\n優ちゃんもやり慣れてて書きやすそうだし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rather than something completely original‚\nsecondary creation feels easier for Yu-chan to write too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.1965074698,
      "endTime": 37.8612468879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.0479137261
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "にじそうさく？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Secondary… creation?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0479137261,
      "endTime": 40.5279137929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん、そこは深く追求せんでええよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan‚ you don’t need to dig into that too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.7145804405,
      "endTime": 44.9945804596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.1945805073
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "上演時間が短いから、シンプルなお話がいいよね？\n短くて、分かりやすくて、有名な話……桃太郎とか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since the runtime is short‚ a simple story is better‚ right?\nShort‚ easy to understand‚ and famous… like Momotaro?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.1945805073,
      "endTime": 58.0026752949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.1893420379
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "幼稚園のお遊戯会じゃありませんのよ\n桃太郎なんて、いくらなんでも幼稚過ぎますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This isn’t a kindergarten recital‚ you know.\nMomotaro is far too childish.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.1893420379,
      "endTime": 65.8176868598,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.0310200214
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことあらへんよ。日本一有名な歌劇団の第一回\n公演は、桃太郎を原作としたミュージカルやったんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not true at all. The very first performance\nof Japan’s most famous opera troupe was a Momotaro-based musical.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.0310200214,
      "endTime": 75.4014278888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.6147609551
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "桃太郎は由緒ある舞台演目の一つ……\n劇団★見の初公演に桃太郎、ありやと思います！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Momotaro is a historically respected stage piece…\nI think Momotaro is a solid choice for Troupe★Hoshimi’s debut!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.6147609551,
      "endTime": 83.94437540359999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.1510420322
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "桃太郎か……\nもしやるとしたら、誰にどの役が似合うかなぁ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Momotaro…\nIf we did it‚ who would suit which role~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.1510420322,
      "endTime": 91.3090919016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.5224251587
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "桃太郎は座長の雫ちゃんがやるとして、お供の犬が\nさくらちゃん、キジが琴乃ちゃん、猿がすずちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan would be Momotaro‚ Sakura-chan as the dog‚\nKotono-chan as the pheasant‚ and Suzu-chan as the monkey…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.5224251587,
      "endTime": 100.46859291390001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.6819259802
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "どうして私が猿なんですの！　うっきー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why am I the monkey!? Ooh-eeh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.6819259802,
      "endTime": 105.04387857120001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.250545152
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "桃太郎をやるなら鬼も必要……強く美しく厳しい鬼……\nそんな鬼にぴったりな人は……莉央さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we do Momotaro‚ we need an oni too… strong‚ beautiful‚ and strict…\nSomeone perfect for that would be… Rio-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.250545152,
      "endTime": 116.2615198453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.4681866646
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "雫はいっぺん莉央さんに怒られるといいのですわ\n鬼を体感出来ますわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku‚ you should get scolded by Rio-san sometime.\nYou’ll really experience what an oni is like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4681866646,
      "endTime": 123.5068260193,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.6934926669
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "桃太郎がダメなら、浦島太郎はどうかな？\n私、カメさんの着ぐるみ着て頑張るよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Momotaro’s no good‚ how about Urashima Taro?\nI’ll do my best wearing a turtle costume!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.6934926669,
      "endTime": 131.5334926288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.7201594671
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "二本足で歩くカメさん着ぐるみ……\n魚魚っとさんみたいで可愛いと思わない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A turtle costume walking on two legs…\nDon’t you think it’s cute‚ like Gyogyotto-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.7201594671,
      "endTime": 138.94952462519998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.1495245298
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "思いませんわよ！　むしろ不気味ですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not at all! It’s downright creepy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.1495245298,
      "endTime": 143.2983681043,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.5050346852
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "配役は、雫ちゃんが浦島太郎、琴乃ちゃんが乙姫様\nさくらちゃんがカメで、すずちゃんは……玉手箱？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Casting-wise‚ Shizuku-chan as Urashima Taro‚\nSakura-chan as the turtle‚ and Suzu-chan as… the jeweled box?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.5050346852,
      "endTime": 154.67805008890002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.871383365
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
